   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="Hs-30885,71_002"/>Herrn Hugo von Hofmannsthal</addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">kuk Ltnd i. d. R. des kuk VIII. Ulan-Rgmts</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb45274" type="place">Czortków</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb644" type="place">Galizien</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="Hs-30885,71_001"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs ref="#pmb35499" type="place">Liechtensteinklamm</rs></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="Hs-30885,71_001"/>Schöne Radtour: ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tern <add place="above"><time>Nachm</time></add><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb35493" type="place">Steinach</rs> bis <rs ref="#pmb35496" type="place">Schladming</rs>; <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00823-1"/>heute<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00823-1">Die beschriebenen Ausflüge und das Treffen
                  mit den <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11737 #pmb18404" subtype="implied">Eltern</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb10863" type="person">Hofmannsthals</rs> erlauben die Datierung auf
                  den <date>18. 7. 1898</date>.</note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Vormitt</time><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb35496" type="place">Schladming</rs>, bis zur <rs ref="#pmb35499" type="place">Liechten<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>teinkla<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c></rs>; heut abends werd ich wohl in der <rs ref="#pmb305739" type="place">Fu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ch</rs>
               Ihre <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11737 #pmb18404" subtype="implied">Eltern</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehn. Seien Sie herzlich gegrüßt. Ihr
                  <signed>Arth.</signed></p></div>
      </body>
